          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1640091479390-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausage meatballs are brown, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> to the pan along with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 7-8 min or until soft</p><p>Once soft, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
