    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>to a large bowl along with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper then add it to the bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
