      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>sausage & mushroom linguine</strong> with the <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
